{code:java}
http://{{host}}:{{port}}/{{context}}/rest/experimental/search?cql=user+~+"Alli"&start=0&limit=10&excerpt=highlight{code}
the returned profilePicture path looks like:
{code:java}
/confluence/s/en_GB/7400/NOCACHE/_/confluence/download/attachments/2150891536/allisonpfeffer_avatar{code}
This is incorrect, and leads to a broken image. The path should be:
